-----------------------
***dm_industrial***
\!/ ALPHA RELEASE \!/
created by black_hawk
-----------------------
     This map is inspired by aim_ag_texture2, one of my favourite map on counter-strike:source, but at the end, I was fed up the orange colour, so I decided to do an official release of this map... 
     The plan of the map still the same, but with a lot of improvement, and without this horrible dev texture... And with a lot of snow ! YEAAAAAAAH !


WARNING, this is an *Alpha* release

Compilation settings :
BSP  = "Normal"
Vvis = "Fast"
Vrad = "Fast"

Stable release but some bugs still...

Features :
-Full 32 players support
-minor optimisation
-basic mesh navigation
-NAV file included
-bugs maps (please report, I've found some of them, but not all...)



Please, help me in my work by feedback and commentaries,
the beta version will be a lot better :)
